---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<Layout
	title="Ready Set Gem - Card Restoration"
	description="Trading card restoration service. We carefully restore your cards with detailed inspection and honest communication. Based in Kingston, Ontario."
>
	<a
		href="#main"
		class="sr-only focus:not-sr-only focus:fixed focus:left-4 focus:top-4 focus:z-50 rounded border border-amber-600 bg-amber-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-amber-900 shadow-lg"
	>
		Skip to content
	</a>

	<header class="sticky top-0 z-40 border-b border-amber-200/60 bg-amber-50/80 backdrop-blur-sm">
		<div class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-5xl items-center justify-between px-5 py-4">
			<a href="/" class="group flex items-center gap-2.5 font-bold tracking-tight text-amber-900">
				<span
					aria-hidden="true"
					class="h-5 w-5 rounded border-2 border-amber-700 bg-amber-100"
				></span>
				<span class="text-base sm:text-lg">Ready Set Gem</span>
			</a>

			<nav class="hidden items-center gap-2 sm:flex" aria-label="Primary">
				<a class="rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-amber-900/80 hover:bg-amber-100/60" href="#how-it-works">How It Works</a>
				<a class="rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-amber-900/80 hover:bg-amber-100/60" href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
				<a class="rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-amber-900/80 hover:bg-amber-100/60" href="#faq">FAQ</a>
				<a
					class="ml-1 rounded-lg border-2 border-amber-700 bg-amber-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-amber-700"
					href="#contact"
				>
					Get Started
				</a>
			</nav>

			<a
				class="sm:hidden rounded-lg border-2 border-amber-700 bg-amber-600 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-amber-700"
				href="#contact"
			>
				Get Started
			</a>
		</div>
	</header>

	<main id="main">
		<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-12 sm:py-16">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl px-5">
				<div class="paper-card paper-texture rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-800">
						Serving collectors across North America
					</p>
					<h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-amber-950 sm:text-5xl">
						We Restore Trading Cards
					</h1>
					<p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-amber-900/90 sm:text-xl">
						Whether it's a childhood favorite that got a little rough, or something you picked up that needs attention, we take the time to understand what's happening with your card before we do anything.
					</p>

					<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
						<a
							class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border-2 border-amber-700 bg-amber-600 px-6 py-3 text-base font-bold text-white shadow-md hover:bg-amber-700"
							href="#contact"
						>
							Send us your cards
						</a>
						<a
							class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border-2 border-amber-300 bg-amber-50 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-amber-900 hover:bg-amber-100"
							href="#how-it-works"
						>
							Learn how it works
						</a>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3" role="list" aria-label="Key details">
						<div class="rounded-full border border-amber-300 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-amber-900" role="listitem">
							<strong class="font-bold">$50 per card</strong>, minimum 5 cards
						</div>
						<div class="rounded-full border border-amber-300 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-amber-900" role="listitem">
							<strong class="font-bold">7–14 days</strong> turnaround
						</div>
						<div class="rounded-full border border-amber-300 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-amber-900" role="listitem">
							<strong class="font-bold">You approve</strong> the plan first
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-12" id="getting-started" aria-label="Getting started">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl px-5">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-950">Getting started</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-lg text-amber-900/80">
					If you’re a collector sending valuable cards, the main question is “what happens before I ship anything?” This is the flow from first message to cards back in hand.
				</p>

				<div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3">
					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">1) Email photos first</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
							Send a few clear photos and a short description of the damage and your goal (display, collection, or grading). We’ll reply with next steps and whether restoration looks realistic.
						</p>
						<ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-amber-900/80">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
								<span>Front + back, straight-on</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
								<span>Close-ups of bends/creases/edge issues</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
								<span>Any prior damage notes (water, smoke, adhesive, etc.)</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">2) We send shipping instructions</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
							After we review your photos, we’ll confirm if we can take the job and share the exact shipping address and packing checklist. This prevents surprise shipments and reduces risk in transit.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-amber-900/70">
							We strongly recommend tracked shipping. For higher-value cards, consider insurance and signature on delivery.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">3) Inspection → plan → approval</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
							Once your cards arrive, we do a close inspection and send a restoration plan with risks and recommendations. <strong class="font-semibold text-amber-950">No work starts until you approve</strong>.
						</p>
						<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-amber-900/70">
							If you decide not to proceed, we can return your cards. Details are shared with your plan so you can make a clear call.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="mt-6 paper-card-elevated rounded-xl border-2 border-amber-400 p-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">Typical response time</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
						We reply to new requests within <strong class="font-semibold text-amber-950">1–2 business days</strong>. If you have a deadline (event, gift, show), mention it in your email and we’ll tell you what’s realistic.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-12" id="how-it-works" aria-label="How it works">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl px-5">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-950">How we work</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-lg text-amber-900/80">
					No surprises. We look closely, we explain what we see, and we only work on what you're comfortable with.
				</p>

				<div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">We inspect everything</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
							Under magnification and UV light. Surface, edges, corners, and how the card stock behaves. Understanding the full picture helps us work safely.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">We tell you what we found</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
							Here's what we found, what we can fix, what the risks are, and what we won't touch. You decide if we proceed.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">We document it all</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
							Before photos, after photos, and careful notes. Your cards are packaged securely for return shipping.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-12" id="what-we-do">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl px-5">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-950">What we can help with</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-lg text-amber-900/80">
					We work on Pokémon, Yu-Gi-Oh!, Magic: The Gathering, sports cards, and other trading cards. Here's what we typically work on.
				</p>

				<div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">Common fixes</h3>
						<ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-amber-900/80">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
								<span>Surface cleaning for dirt, fingerprints, and handling marks</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
								<span>Light warping or bends</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
								<span>Minor adhesive residue</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
								<span>Edge roughness or lifting</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-amber-900/70">
							Every card is different. We'll assess yours and be honest about what's possible.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="paper-card-elevated rounded-xl border-2 border-amber-400 p-6">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">What we won't do</h3>
						<ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-amber-900/80">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-800"></span>
								<span>Trim, sand, or reshape corners or edges</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-800"></span>
								<span>Add color, touch up ink, or simulate printing</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-800"></span>
								<span>Anything meant to fool grading companies</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-amber-900">
							We're here to restore, not alter. If something looks like it would be flagged as alteration, we'll tell you upfront.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-12" id="process">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl px-5">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-950">The process</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-lg text-amber-900/80">
					From the moment your cards arrive until they're on their way back. We expect 7–14 days, but turnaround could be longer based on our queue, how many cards you send, and the damage on each card.
				</p>

				<div class="mt-6 paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">How updates + approval work</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
						Everything is documented in writing so you can make a clear decision. We communicate by email unless we agree on something else.
					</p>
					<ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-amber-900/80">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
							<span><strong class="font-semibold text-amber-950">You receive:</strong> photos + findings + a recommended plan, with risks and what we will/won’t do.</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
							<span><strong class="font-semibold text-amber-950">You approve:</strong> by replying in writing (or via a simple confirmation method we provide).</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
							<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
							<span><strong class="font-semibold text-amber-950">No surprises:</strong> if we discover something new during work, we pause and check in before continuing.</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-amber-600 bg-amber-50 text-sm font-bold text-amber-900">
								1
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">Your cards arrive</h3>
								<p class="mt-1 text-amber-900/80">
									We log everything, take consistent photos under good lighting, and make initial notes about condition.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-amber-600 bg-amber-50 text-sm font-bold text-amber-900">
								2
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">Close inspection</h3>
								<p class="mt-1 text-amber-900/80">
									Magnification and UV light check. We look at surface, edges, corners, and how the card stock behaves. This helps us determine what's safe to work on.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-amber-600 bg-amber-50 text-sm font-bold text-amber-900">
								3
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">We send you a plan</h3>
								<p class="mt-1 text-amber-900/80">
									Here's what we found, what we think we can do, what the risks are, and what we recommend. You review and approve before we start any work.
								</p>
								<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-amber-900/70">
									If you want changes (for example, “only clean, no stabilization”), tell us. We’ll adjust the plan or recommend against parts that aren’t safe.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-amber-600 bg-amber-50 text-sm font-bold text-amber-900">
								4
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">We do the work</h3>
								<p class="mt-1 text-amber-900/80">
									Once you approve, we proceed carefully. Controlled cleaning, stabilization when needed, and conservative methods throughout.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-amber-600 bg-amber-50 text-sm font-bold text-amber-900">
								5
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">Final photos and return</h3>
								<p class="mt-1 text-amber-900/80">
									We photograph the results, package everything securely, and arrange return shipping with tracking.
								</p>
								<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-amber-900/70">
									You’ll receive tracking when your package ships. If you’d like insurance or signature on delivery, tell us and we’ll include options.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="mt-6 paper-card-elevated rounded-xl border-2 border-amber-400 p-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">If you decide not to proceed</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
						If the risks don’t feel worth it, that’s okay. We’ll return your cards safely. Return shipping is billed at cost with tracking, and any inspection/handling fees (if applicable) are communicated up front so you’re never surprised.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-12" id="after-care-report">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl px-5">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-950">Your after-care report</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-lg text-amber-900/80">
					Every card you send back comes with a detailed report. Photos, findings, and a clear picture of what changed.
				</p>

				<div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">Comprehensive documentation</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
							Your report includes before and after photos under consistent lighting, showing exactly what we found and what changed. We document everything we observed during inspection and restoration.
						</p>
						<ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-amber-900/80">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
								<span>High-resolution before and after photos</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
								<span>Detailed notes on condition and findings</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
								<span>Documentation of work performed</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">Magnification and UV analysis</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
							We use magnification and UV/blacklight to reveal imperfections that aren't visible to the naked eye. These images are included in your report, highlighting issues like surface scratches, hidden residue, or card stock anomalies.
						</p>
						<ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-amber-900/80">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
								<span>Magnified views showing surface details</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
								<span>UV/blacklight images highlighting imperfections</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
								<span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-amber-600"></span>
								<span>Edge and corner condition documentation</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="mt-6 paper-card-elevated rounded-xl border-2 border-amber-400 p-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">Surface condition assessment</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
						For each card, we document the surface condition before and after restoration. This gives you a clear comparison of what changed and what remains.
					</p>
					<div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
						<div class="rounded-lg border border-amber-300 bg-amber-50/50 p-4">
							<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-900">Before restoration</p>
							<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-amber-900/80">Documented surface condition, imperfections, and any visible damage</p>
						</div>
						<div class="rounded-lg border border-amber-300 bg-amber-50/50 p-4">
							<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-900">After restoration</p>
							<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-amber-900/80">Current surface state, improvements made, and any remaining characteristics</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="mt-6 paper-card rounded-xl p-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">Category-by-category grading</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
						Your report includes before and after assessments across key grading categories, giving you a clear view of how each aspect of the card changed.
					</p>
					<div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
						<div class="rounded-lg border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50/30 p-4">
							<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2">
								<span class="font-semibold text-amber-950">Surface</span>
								<div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
									<span class="text-amber-900/70">Before:</span>
									<span class="font-bold text-amber-900">6</span>
									<span class="text-amber-900/60">→</span>
									<span class="text-amber-900/70">After:</span>
									<span class="font-bold text-amber-900">8</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="rounded-lg border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50/30 p-4">
							<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2">
								<span class="font-semibold text-amber-950">Edges</span>
								<div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
									<span class="text-amber-900/70">Before:</span>
									<span class="font-bold text-amber-900">5</span>
									<span class="text-amber-900/60">→</span>
									<span class="text-amber-900/70">After:</span>
									<span class="font-bold text-amber-900">7</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="rounded-lg border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50/30 p-4">
							<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2">
								<span class="font-semibold text-amber-950">Corners</span>
								<div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
									<span class="text-amber-900/70">Before:</span>
									<span class="font-bold text-amber-900">7</span>
